@micah_sudduth thank you so much for your kind words. We too are looking forward to see this journey unfold. Since I play one of the characters in the show, I'm nervous to the T. Im hoping the studio let's the world grade our product. Do follow the show and your 2 cents would be highly appreciated.

This looks fun, look forward to following the journey. If you’re planning to do festivals, we @thebobbilliams just wrapped up our run with our series “Home” and know the process is a lot. So if you need any insights, happy to give my 2 cents.
@ushaswini_fotography yeah. I'm glad you have Hotstar. It starts early July.

This is refreshing and awesome!!!! Congratulations Gav!!!! 🎊😊 this is so kool!! I had just started watching office again.. two days ago.. binging.. n now this.. curious to know what part you are playing 🙂🙃😊 for once am so happy we have Hotstar !! When will it start airing?
Congrats Gavin .Looking forward to watch it
@simrinvijayakar no no don't cry little girl. There will be happy moments to cherish.
Good luck @methashutter !!! Oh my the set got me super nostalgic! 🙈 I might just cry in bits while watching this heheh.
Gav, am so proud of you. seriously.
